Package: pTRAPPING
Title: A Suite of Functions for the Analyses of PhosphoTRAP Data in R
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Camilo", "Rodríguez", , "camo.rodriguez@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a toolkit for the analysis of PhosphoTRAP sequencing data, including preprocessing, 
    differential expression analysis, and visualization. Implements streamlined workflows and offers functions for
    generating publication-ready tables and plots in few lines of code, enabling reproducible and efficient 
    exploration of PhosphoTRAP datasets.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
